OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1782910144
OL,3,CWomen with PMOS to have annual review
OL,4,Cof symptoms and long-term health risks
OL,6,FWords by ITV News Producer Lucy
OL,7,FFitzsimons
OL,9,FMillions of women with polyendocrine
OL,10,Fmetabolic ovarian syndrome (PMOS) will
OL,11,Fbe offered an annual review to help
OL,12,Fmonitor their condition, following
OL,13,Fdraft guidelines issued by the
OL,14,FNational Institute for Health and Care
OL,15,FExcellence (Nice).
OL,17,FPMOS - formerly known as polycystic
OL,18,Fovarian syndrome (PCOS) - is a
OL,19,Fcomplex, lifelong endocrine condition
OL,20,Fthat affects between three and four
OL,21,Fmillion women in the UK.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
