FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1782910144
OL,3,CWomen with PMOS to have annual review
OL,4,Cof symptoms and long-term health risks
OL,6,FCommon symptoms include irregular or
OL,7,Fabsent periods, acne, weight gain, and
OL,8,Fboth excessive hair growth and hair
OL,9,Floss.
OL,11,FIt also carries an increased risk of
OL,12,Flonger-term health problems, including
OL,13,Ftype 2 diabetes, endometrial cancer,
OL,14,Fand cardiovascular disease.
OL,16,FDespite this, experts say it is
OL,17,Ffrequently underdiagnosed and
OL,18,Finconsistently managed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1782910144
OL,3,CWomen with PMOS to have annual review
OL,4,Cof symptoms and long-term health risks
OL,6,FLast September, a report by the PMOS
OL,7,FAll-Party Parliamentary Group (APPG)
OL,8,Ffound that women with the condition
OL,9,Fwere facing prolonged delays in
OL,10,Fdiagnosis, fragmented care, and
OL,11,Flimited access to treatments - with
OL,12,Fmany turning to social media for
OL,13,Fanswers.
OL,15,FNow, for the first time, Nice has
OL,16,Fpublished draft guidelines on PMOS,
OL,17,Fwhere health officials have called for
OL,18,Fthe condition to be diagnosed sooner,
OL,19,Fas well as an annual review for those
OL,20,Fwho have already been diagnosed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1782910144
OL,3,CWomen with PMOS to have annual review
OL,4,Cof symptoms and long-term health risks
OL,6,FThis yearly review would look at the
OL,7,Fwomen's symptoms and "any concerns
OL,8,Fthey have about period regularity,
OL,9,Ffertility, weight, mood and sleep
OL,10,Fapnoea".
OL,12,FIt would also assess any use of
OL,13,Fmedication and look at the
OL,14,Findividual's long-term health risks,
OL,15,Fsuch as cardiovascular disease or
OL,16,Fdiabetes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1782910144
OL,3,CWomen with PMOS to have annual review
OL,4,Cof symptoms and long-term health risks
OL,6,FThe draft guidelines also recommend
OL,7,Fthat all women with irregular or
OL,8,Fabsent menstrual cycles and symptoms
OL,9,For signs of excessive levels of male
OL,10,Fhormones should be investigated for
OL,11,FPMOS.
OL,13,FIt also made several other
OL,14,Frecommendations on fertility care,
OL,15,Fmental health, and long-term health
OL,16,Frisks linked to the condition.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1782910144
OL,3,CWomen with PMOS to have annual review
OL,4,Cof symptoms and long-term health risks
OL,6,FBut the guidelines do not recommend
OL,7,Flaser or light therapies for women who
OL,8,Fhave excess hair growth linked to the
OL,9,Fcondition, known as hirsutism, with
OL,10,FNice saying that this could cost the
OL,11,FNHS up to #100 million per year in
OL,12,FEngland.
OL,14,FThe guidelines say there is a "lack of
OL,15,Fclinical evidence and uncertainty
OL,16,Fabout cost-effectiveness" for these
OL,17,Ftreatments.
OL,26,@vD@_OUxD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1782910144
OL,3,CWomen with PMOS to have annual review
OL,4,Cof symptoms and long-term health risks
OL,6,FHowever, it makes a number of other
OL,7,Frecommendations to tackle hirsutism,
OL,8,Fincluding the use of a contraceptive
OL,9,Fpill.
OL,11,FCaroline Andrews, a volunteer trustee
OL,12,Fat the PMOS charity Verity, welcomes
OL,13,Fthese guidelines, but says she hopes
OL,14,Fit doesn't lead to a "postcode
OL,15,Flottery" in care
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1782910144
OL,3,CWomen with PMOS to have annual review
OL,4,Cof symptoms and long-term health risks
OL,6,FVerity, a charity set up to raise
OL,7,Fawareness about PMOS, welcomed the
OL,8,Fannouncement but said it was
OL,9,Fdisappointing that it had taken Nice
OL,10,Fso long to publish guidelines about a
OL,11,Fcondition which affects one in eight
OL,12,Fwomen.
OL,14,FVolunteer trustee Caroline Andrews
OL,15,Fcalled the introduction of annual
OL,16,Freviews a "real triumph".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
