FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1782910144
OL,3,CWomen with PMOS to have annual review
OL,4,Cof symptoms and long-term health risks
OL,6,FShe told ITV News: "To have annual
OL,7,Freviews to look at these issues, to
OL,8,Flook at how this is impacting those
OL,9,Fpatients with the condition, is
OL,10,Freally, really important.
OL,12,F"And we'd like to see that this then
OL,13,Fhelps the patients and professionals
OL,14,Flead to a more proactive, preventative
OL,15,Fapproach to their condition."
OL,17,FShe added: "It's going to give a sense
OL,18,Fof validation, as well that this is
OL,19,Fsomething that needs to be considered
OL,20,Fas a chronic lifelong condition."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1782910144
OL,3,CWomen with PMOS to have annual review
OL,4,Cof symptoms and long-term health risks
OL,6,FMarie Anne Ledingham, a consultant
OL,7,Fclinical adviser for women's and
OL,8,Freproductive health at Nice, said:
OL,9,F"PMOS is a common but often overlooked
OL,10,Fcondition that can have a major impact
OL,11,Fon health and well-being.
OL,13,F"Recommending a simple annual review
OL,14,Fis an important step towards ensuring
OL,15,Fpeople get the ongoing care and
OL,16,Fmonitoring they need.
OL,26,@qD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1782910144
OL,3,CWomen with PMOS to have annual review
OL,4,Cof symptoms and long-term health risks
OL,6,F"This new guideline will help improve
OL,7,Fconsistency of care, increase
OL,8,Fawareness of the condition, and
OL,9,Fsupport earlier diagnosis and
OL,10,Fmanagement."
OL,12,FThe new draft guidelines come a month
OL,13,Fafter the new name for PMOS was
OL,14,Fannounced.
OL,16,FThe name change was described as a
OL,17,F"watershed moment" in women's health,
OL,18,Fwith the hope that it will improve
OL,19,Fdiagnosis and attract more funding and
OL,20,Fresearch into the condition.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
