OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31512
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1782910144
OL,3,CWomen with PMOS to have annual review
OL,4,Cof symptoms and long-term health risks
OL,6,FExperts said the new name is
OL,7,F"reflective of the fact that it's an
OL,8,Fendocrine condition with metabolic
OL,9,Fconsequences", instead of the main
OL,10,Ffocus being on the reproductive
OL,11,Faspects.
